headline: Camden: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The real estate investment trust, based in Houston, said it had funds from operations of $193.1 million, or $1.76 per share, in the period. The average estimate of six analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $1.73 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
